section Section1;

  Source = Oracle.Database("COHREP", [CommandTimeout = #duration(0, 0, 10, 0), Query = "
  SELECT
    sysdate                                                                     extract_date,

    tb.*
FROM
    xxcoh.xxcoh_m2_report_tb tb

        1 = 1

        SELECT
            period_year - "&YearOffset&"

            gl.gl_periods gp

            trunc(sysdate) BETWEEN gp.start_date AND gp.end_date
